        <abstract> 
<p>CD’s letter [<hi rend="doubleUnderline">7922</hi>] was very sweet to her, and if her marriage [to Richard B. Litchfield] can be half as perfect as CD’s she will be very happy.</p> 
            <p>Richard’s German fails in communicating with washerwomen.</p>
